title: First-Line Supervisors of Production and Operating Workers
descr: Directly supervise and coordinate the activities of production and operating workers, such as inspectors, precision workers, machine setters and operators, assemblers, fabricators, and plant and system operators. Excludes team or work leaders.

experience: Previous work-related skill, knowledge, or experience is required for these occupations. For example, an electrician must have completed three or four years of apprenticeship or several years of vocational training, and often must have passed a licensing exam, in order to perform the job.
education: Most occupations in this zone require training in vocational schools, related on-the-job experience, or an associate's degree.
job_training: Employees in these occupations usually need one or two years of training involving both on-the-job experience and informal training with experienced workers. A recognized apprenticeship program may be associated with these occupations.
example: These occupations usually involve using communication and organizational skills to coordinate, supervise, manage, or train others to accomplish goals. Examples include hydroelectric production managers, desktop publishers, electricians, agricultural technicians, barbers, court reporters and simultaneous captioners, and medical assistants.

work_tasks.title: First-Line Supervisors of Production and Operating Workers
work_tasks.task: Enforce safety and sanitation regulations.
work_tasks.descr: Enforce safety and sanitation regulations.

work_tasks.title: First-Line Supervisors of Production and Operating Workers
work_tasks.task: Keep records of employees' attendance and hours worked.
work_tasks.descr: Keep records of employees' attendance and hours worked.

work_tasks.title: First-Line Supervisors of Production and Operating Workers
work_tasks.task: Inspect materials, products, or equipment to detect defects or malfunctions.
work_tasks.descr: Inspect materials, products, or equipment to detect defects or malfunctions.

work_tasks.title: First-Line Supervisors of Production and Operating Workers
work_tasks.task: Interpret specifications, blueprints, job orders, and company policies and procedures for workers.
work_tasks.descr: Interpret specifications, blueprints, job orders, and company policies and procedures for workers.

work_tasks.title: First-Line Supervisors of Production and Operating Workers
work_tasks.task: Observe work and monitor gauges, dials, and other indicators to ensure that operators conform to production or processing standards.
work_tasks.descr: Observe work and monitor gauges, dials, and other indicators to ensure that operators conform to production or processing standards.

work_tasks.title: First-Line Supervisors of Production and Operating Workers
work_tasks.task: Read and analyze charts, work orders, production schedules, and other records and reports to determine production requirements and to evaluate current production estimates and outputs.
work_tasks.descr: Read and analyze charts, work orders, production schedules, and other records and reports to determine production requirements and to evaluate current production estimates and outputs.

work_tasks.title: First-Line Supervisors of Production and Operating Workers
work_tasks.task: Plan and establish work schedules, assignments, and production sequences to meet production goals.
work_tasks.descr: Plan and establish work schedules, assignments, and production sequences to meet production goals.

work_tasks.title: First-Line Supervisors of Production and Operating Workers
work_tasks.task: Confer with other supervisors to coordinate operations and activities within or between departments.
work_tasks.descr: Confer with other supervisors to coordinate operations and activities within or between departments.

work_tasks.title: First-Line Supervisors of Production and Operating Workers
work_tasks.task: Set up and adjust machines and equipment.
work_tasks.descr: Set up and adjust machines and equipment.

work_tasks.title: First-Line Supervisors of Production and Operating Workers
work_tasks.task: Direct and coordinate the activities of employees engaged in the production or processing of goods, such as inspectors, machine setters, or fabricators.
work_tasks.descr: Direct and coordinate the activities of employees engaged in the production or processing of goods, such as inspectors, machine setters, or fabricators.

work_tasks.title: First-Line Supervisors of Production and Operating Workers
work_tasks.task: Conduct employee training in equipment operations or work and safety procedures, or assign employee training to experienced workers.
work_tasks.descr: Conduct employee training in equipment operations or work and safety procedures, or assign employee training to experienced workers.

work_tasks.title: First-Line Supervisors of Production and Operating Workers
work_tasks.task: Evaluate employee performance.
work_tasks.descr: Evaluate employee performance.

work_tasks.title: First-Line Supervisors of Production and Operating Workers
work_tasks.task: Determine standards, budgets, production goals, and rates, based on company policies, equipment and labor availability, and workloads.
work_tasks.descr: Determine standards, budgets, production goals, and rates, based on company policies, equipment and labor availability, and workloads.

work_tasks.title: First-Line Supervisors of Production and Operating Workers
work_tasks.task: Confer with management or subordinates to resolve worker problems, complaints, or grievances.
work_tasks.descr: Confer with management or subordinates to resolve worker problems, complaints, or grievances.

work_tasks.title: First-Line Supervisors of Production and Operating Workers
work_tasks.task: Calculate labor and equipment requirements and production specifications, using standard formulas.
work_tasks.descr: Calculate labor and equipment requirements and production specifications, using standard formulas.

work_tasks.title: First-Line Supervisors of Production and Operating Workers
work_tasks.task: Recommend or implement measures to motivate employees and to improve production methods, equipment performance, product quality, or efficiency.
work_tasks.descr: Recommend or implement measures to motivate employees and to improve production methods, equipment performance, product quality, or efficiency.

work_tasks.task: Maintain operations data, such as time, production, and cost records, and prepare management reports of production results.
work_tasks.descr: Maintain operations data, such as time, production, and cost records, and prepare management reports of production results.

work_tasks.task: Requisition materials, supplies, equipment parts, or repair services.
